    "body": "You could use the [analytics API](https://www.algolia.com/doc/rest-api/analytics/) but it's not meant for heavy traffic. So if you find a way to cache those results in your backend, you could serve them in your front-end.\r\n\r\nThe short answer is that we do not provide such feature at the moment.",
